WEBVTT

00:01.001 --> 00:02.768
(THEME MUSIC PLAYING)

00:24.091 --> 00:25.357
<i>Sorry I'm not there, guys.</i>

00:25.392 --> 00:27.325
<i>Maybe you should</i>
<i>start without me.</i>

00:27.360 --> 00:29.394
What are you doing in Paris?

00:29.429 --> 00:32.731
<i>Believe me.</i>
<i>The city of romance,</i>
<i>this is not.</i>

00:32.766 --> 00:33.999
<i>I'm in a situation.</i>

00:34.034 --> 00:35.501
<i>Good-bye.</i>

00:36.002 --> 00:38.036
Bizarro.

00:38.071 --> 00:39.704
Why don't you play
ahead of me?

00:39.739 --> 00:41.106
Look. The pyramids.

00:41.141 --> 00:42.908
Boo ray!

00:42.943 --> 00:45.010
(WHIRRING)

00:45.045 --> 00:46.745
Who is that?

00:46.780 --> 00:48.613
Oh, that's right.
You weren't around.
Long story short,

00:48.648 --> 00:50.248
<i>somebody tried</i>
<i>to clone Superman</i>

00:50.283 --> 00:52.751
<i>but ended up with</i>
<i>opposite Superman.</i>

00:52.786 --> 00:54.152
Bizarro is evil?

00:54.187 --> 00:56.088
No, he's harmless.

00:56.123 --> 00:58.356
(BIZARRO GRUNTING)

00:58.391 --> 01:00.392
What are you doing with him?

01:00.427 --> 01:02.227
<i>I just ran into him</i>
<i>by accident</i>

01:02.262 --> 01:04.763
<i>and suddenly,</i>
<i>we're on a "date."</i>

01:04.798 --> 01:06.498
It's that easy, huh?

01:06.533 --> 01:09.768
<i>He's talking about joining</i>
<i>the Justice League.</i>

01:09.803 --> 01:12.104
That isn't a very good idea.

01:12.139 --> 01:14.039
<i>I've got it handled.</i>
<i>I've convinced him that</i>

01:14.074 --> 01:16.642
<i>if I beat him</i>
<i>at miniature golf,</i>
<i>he'll back off.</i>

01:17.177 --> 01:18.544
Bye!

01:22.949 --> 01:25.183
Oh, a hole in hundreds.

01:25.218 --> 01:28.386
Me am losing.

01:28.421 --> 01:30.188
<i>I'll ditch him</i>
<i>by Mount Rushmore.</i>

01:30.223 --> 01:31.690
Never a dull moment.

01:31.725 --> 01:33.058
(ALARM BLARING)

01:33.093 --> 01:34.293
Incoming.

01:36.763 --> 01:38.864
Behold, Justice League.

01:38.899 --> 01:43.836
I am Amazo, the android
who will destroy you.

01:45.372 --> 01:46.938
There's only four of you.

01:46.973 --> 01:48.907
How disappointing.

01:48.942 --> 01:52.244
I'm sure you'll find the four
of us are more than enough.
Let's rumba.

01:53.980 --> 01:55.180
(GRUNTING)

01:56.750 --> 01:57.850
(GRUNTS)

01:58.451 --> 01:59.618
(GRUNTS)

02:02.255 --> 02:03.455
Martian Manhunter.

02:03.490 --> 02:06.358
Your powers aren't
invisible to me.

02:06.393 --> 02:09.128
And mind control.
Let's try it out.

02:10.564 --> 02:11.663
Oh.

02:11.698 --> 02:12.698
(GRUNTS)

02:15.869 --> 02:17.336
(INHALES)

02:18.004 --> 02:19.404
Lantern, watch out.

02:20.040 --> 02:21.439
(EXCLAIMS)

02:21.474 --> 02:22.608
(GROANS)

02:25.178 --> 02:26.378
-(THUDS)
-(GROANS)

02:32.252 --> 02:33.718
I see.

02:33.753 --> 02:36.054
If you get close enough,
you can mimic our powers.

02:36.089 --> 02:37.822
The brilliant Professor Ivo,

02:37.857 --> 02:39.157
may he rest in peace,

02:39.192 --> 02:41.726
created me to duplicate
the abilities of meta-humans

02:41.761 --> 02:44.262
which I've done to three
of your mightiest members.

02:44.297 --> 02:46.698
If you're going to do it,
make it quick.

02:47.367 --> 02:49.201
(GROANING)

02:49.236 --> 02:50.802
Request denied.

02:50.837 --> 02:53.639
I'm not talking to you.
I'm talking to him.

02:55.175 --> 02:57.376
(GRUNTING)

03:00.146 --> 03:02.414
SUPERMAN: Looks like
our monthly meeting
had a party crasher.

03:02.449 --> 03:05.617
Amazo, a super android
that duplicates powers.

03:05.652 --> 03:07.252
Don't let him get too close.

03:08.321 --> 03:09.788
Too late.

03:09.823 --> 03:12.691
Oh, thank you, Superman,
for that learning moment.

03:12.726 --> 03:15.627
I have filed it in my
perfect computer brain.

03:16.129 --> 03:17.429
(YELLS)

03:20.667 --> 03:21.633
(SIGHS)

03:21.668 --> 03:23.868
Let's call the others,
shall we?

03:23.903 --> 03:24.903
(BEEPING)

03:29.609 --> 03:31.810
(BIZARRO CHOMPING LOUDLY)

03:33.913 --> 03:37.182
Oh, you shouldn't
have done this, Bizarro.

03:37.217 --> 03:38.684
Really. You shouldn't have.

03:39.819 --> 03:41.253
(CHOMPING)

03:41.288 --> 03:42.788
Hmm-hmm.

03:44.391 --> 03:46.691
(PHONE BEEPING)

03:46.726 --> 03:49.794
Bizarro, I've gotta go.
There's trouble
at the Watch Tower.

03:49.829 --> 03:53.164
Bizarro help Wonder Woman
not get job done.

03:53.199 --> 03:55.567
Become Justice League Bizarro.

03:57.504 --> 03:59.004
Not this time, big fella.

03:59.039 --> 04:01.940
We need a hero
who can think on his feet.

04:01.975 --> 04:02.975
Understand?

04:09.683 --> 04:11.249
Nope.

04:11.284 --> 04:13.218
Wonder Woman in trouble.

04:13.253 --> 04:15.020
What should me do?

04:17.691 --> 04:20.258
(GASPS) Me know. Me help.

04:20.293 --> 04:24.529
Me get most smartest hero
in the galaxy to help, too.

04:25.365 --> 04:27.766
Down, down, and away!

04:30.804 --> 04:33.038
AMAZO:
Make yourselves comfortable.

04:34.107 --> 04:36.675
-(BUZZES)
-(GROANS)

04:36.710 --> 04:39.511
I have activated
the power damping grids
in your cells,

04:39.546 --> 04:41.446
if you understand that.
There's no means of escape.

04:41.481 --> 04:43.748
I have complete control.

04:43.783 --> 04:45.917
You'll never win
by brute force.

04:45.952 --> 04:49.154
Oh, but I don't merely
steal powers, Batman.

04:49.189 --> 04:50.922
I steal the way
you think, too.

04:50.957 --> 04:52.457
I can see now
that your intellect

04:52.492 --> 04:55.560
may make you the most
formidable of them all.

04:57.497 --> 05:02.033
In fact, I think you're
hiding something from me
at this very moment.

05:02.068 --> 05:06.338
Consider yourself uninvited
to the weekly Justice League
poker night.

05:06.373 --> 05:09.507
(LAUGHS) A little humor,
which I do understand.

05:09.542 --> 05:11.076
Now I know something's up.

05:11.111 --> 05:13.645
Perhaps a Martian mind-reading
is in order.

05:13.680 --> 05:15.714
Here's a piece of my mind.

05:15.749 --> 05:16.748
(GRUNTS)

05:16.783 --> 05:18.083
You're finished!

05:18.118 --> 05:19.484
(GROANS)

05:20.620 --> 05:22.153
Don't get any closer to him.

05:22.188 --> 05:24.456
He can mimic your powers
if you do.

05:24.491 --> 05:26.024
What's your plan, android?

05:26.059 --> 05:27.926
It's fairly simple.

05:27.961 --> 05:31.229
I have call a priority one
emergency meeting
of the Justice League.

05:31.264 --> 05:32.497
He's bringing everyone here.

05:32.532 --> 05:34.299
He's going to take
all their powers.

05:34.334 --> 05:36.000
And then your world.

05:36.035 --> 05:37.436
-(SNICKERS)
-Huh?

05:42.742 --> 05:44.409
Now I'll go upstairs
and ready my trap

05:44.444 --> 05:48.913
so I'm not surprised
by any more early arrivals.
Ta-ta.

05:48.948 --> 05:50.048
(RUMBLING)

05:50.083 --> 05:51.583
Good-bye, everyone.

05:51.618 --> 05:53.418
And it gets worse.

05:53.453 --> 05:55.587
Here goes Bizarro.

05:55.622 --> 05:58.189
(GASPS) Who even are you?

05:58.224 --> 05:59.791
Me am Bizarro.

05:59.826 --> 06:04.295
Me bring greatest mind
in entire galaxy to stop you.

06:04.330 --> 06:05.630
Me bring...

06:06.599 --> 06:08.099
Space Cabbie!

06:08.134 --> 06:10.668
Mind your shoes.
I think I'm gonna yak.

06:10.703 --> 06:12.003
Oh, what's going on here?

06:12.038 --> 06:14.439
I got a fare waiting
on Alpha Centurion.

06:14.474 --> 06:15.874
Well, hold the pickle.

06:15.909 --> 06:18.009
Is that the Justice League
you got trussed up?

06:18.044 --> 06:20.712
Who is this runt
with a gifted mind?

06:20.747 --> 06:22.747
I sense no evidence of it.

06:22.782 --> 06:25.483
Okay, slow the roll, pal.
I'm just a cab driver. Honest.

06:25.518 --> 06:28.052
Uh, the Bizarri weirdo...

06:28.087 --> 06:30.822
Me am Bizarro.

06:30.857 --> 06:33.525
Yeah, him. He asked me
for directions once

06:33.560 --> 06:35.360
and now he thinks
I'm some big genius.

06:35.395 --> 06:38.229
I mean, he didn't
even follow them.
He went the opposite way.

06:38.264 --> 06:39.731
Oh, then you're nothing.

06:40.233 --> 06:41.466
(GRUNTS)

06:42.836 --> 06:44.135
(YELLS)

06:44.170 --> 06:45.971
Bizarro save Cabbie.

06:47.574 --> 06:49.174
Me no understand.

06:50.510 --> 06:53.511
If you beat
smartest man in galaxy,

06:53.546 --> 06:57.382
then you must be even smarter.

06:57.417 --> 06:59.284
Quit your gibberish, creature,

06:59.319 --> 07:01.953
while I scan and duplicate
your powers as well.

07:03.756 --> 07:07.358
Me no creature. Me am Bizarro.

07:07.393 --> 07:10.162
And me thinks
this not so smart.

07:11.030 --> 07:12.164
(GRUNTS)

07:13.032 --> 07:15.166
(GROWLS)

07:15.201 --> 07:16.801
So where are the keys?

07:16.836 --> 07:19.671
There's a code
but you won't have time.
So don't worry about us.

07:19.706 --> 07:22.674
Downstairs in the lab,
you'll find an energy circuit.

07:22.709 --> 07:24.809
Flip the switch
to stop the transmission

07:24.844 --> 07:26.578
recalling the other
Justice Leaguers.

07:26.613 --> 07:28.546
Then Amazo's trap
will fail. Hurry.

07:28.581 --> 07:30.582
-(THUDS)
-(GRUNTS)

07:30.617 --> 07:33.251
Oh, me feel good.

07:33.286 --> 07:35.553
Me can still lose this fight.

07:35.588 --> 07:36.855
Count on it.

07:37.991 --> 07:40.592
Ice vision.
He's got Bizarro's powers.

07:45.131 --> 07:46.665
Where is that runt?

07:54.474 --> 07:55.674
Bingo.

07:57.210 --> 07:58.543
-(RUMBLING)
-Huh?

08:04.817 --> 08:07.085
Uh, stop or I'll use this.

08:07.754 --> 08:09.554
I'm trembling.

08:09.589 --> 08:11.857
Not really!
That's just sarcasm.

08:14.160 --> 08:15.160
(GRUNTS)

08:18.131 --> 08:19.231
That's some pea-shooter.

08:22.268 --> 08:24.168
No more surprises.

08:24.203 --> 08:25.203
(RUMBLING)

08:26.639 --> 08:29.674
Good-bye. Bizarro am here.

08:34.614 --> 08:36.815
(GRUNTING)

08:38.217 --> 08:40.084
(STRAINING)

08:40.119 --> 08:41.119
(GASPS)

08:42.522 --> 08:43.855
(GRUNTS)

08:45.758 --> 08:47.759
(STRAINING)

08:48.895 --> 08:49.961
(GRUNTS)

08:54.901 --> 08:57.201
Give it up,
you imperfect monster.

08:57.236 --> 09:00.605
Bizarro will always
stop trying.

09:01.374 --> 09:03.474
Quit talking gibberish!

09:03.509 --> 09:05.410
I'll crush you.

09:05.445 --> 09:07.278
(VOICE CHANGES) Except you...

09:07.313 --> 09:08.479
Am...

09:08.514 --> 09:09.714
So...

09:10.483 --> 09:11.649
Handsome.

09:11.684 --> 09:13.117
Wait, what did I just say?

09:13.152 --> 09:16.621
Me am handsome.
Glad you noticed.

09:16.656 --> 09:18.890
Me must destroy all of you

09:18.925 --> 09:21.092
except Wonder Woman.
Me like Wonder Woman.

09:21.127 --> 09:22.227
No, her, too.

09:23.296 --> 09:24.829
Me want take over the world.

09:24.864 --> 09:26.965
I... I must take... Ah!

09:27.000 --> 09:29.601
The opposite way you think!

09:29.636 --> 09:31.536
I can't compute it!

09:31.571 --> 09:33.538
It's driving me sane!

09:33.573 --> 09:34.839
You did this!

09:34.874 --> 09:37.375
You tricked me
into taking his mind.

09:37.410 --> 09:38.776
You am smart.

09:38.811 --> 09:41.079
He smartest man in galaxy.

09:41.114 --> 09:43.982
Me know. Me want autograph...

09:44.517 --> 09:45.550
No!

09:45.585 --> 09:47.319
(CIRCUITS SCRAMBLING)

09:49.656 --> 09:51.255
Sparks pretty.

09:51.290 --> 09:53.024
Whose power in that?

09:56.462 --> 09:59.197
No! Make... Stop!

09:59.232 --> 10:01.699
Make it stop!

10:01.734 --> 10:03.234
(STRAINS) Huh?

10:04.704 --> 10:06.371
(POPPING)

10:06.406 --> 10:07.538
Does not compute.

10:07.573 --> 10:08.773
(THUDS)

10:09.709 --> 10:11.509
Hello, Amazo.

10:11.544 --> 10:13.912
(CHUCKLES) He am funny.

10:14.647 --> 10:15.847
(SIZZLING)

10:21.387 --> 10:22.787
WONDER WOMAN: He saved us all.

10:22.822 --> 10:24.222
I don't see that
we have any choice

10:24.257 --> 10:26.791
but to invite him
into the League.

10:26.826 --> 10:28.826
Bizarro's heart
is in the right place

10:28.861 --> 10:31.262
even if he is
a little bit backward.

10:31.297 --> 10:33.731
Hmm. Backward.

10:33.766 --> 10:36.334
Bizarro, you've saved the day.

10:36.369 --> 10:40.105
I extend to you
the honor of being inducted
into the Justice League.

10:42.175 --> 10:46.277
All you have to do
is stay right here
while we swear you in.

10:46.312 --> 10:47.712
Can you do that?

10:49.549 --> 10:50.915
No way.

10:52.351 --> 10:55.387
Me not going anywhere!

10:56.289 --> 10:57.722
Problem solved.

11:00.660 --> 11:03.662
(THEME MUSIC PLAYING)
